creator: Wakanim production
descriptionHtml:
YOUR FAVORITE SHOWS LIVE FROM JAPAN WITH WAKANIM®

Find older titles and newest release in an offer that allows unlimited viewing online in high definition, without any advertising directly on your tablet or Android compatible phone.


Features:
- Watch your episodes in HD
- Watch on you television with Chromecast
- Follow the progress of your episodes
- Search by genre and by popularity directly from the catalog
- Receive notifications for new episode releases or important site updates
- Track your favorite series by previously watched episodes.
- Access all the Wakanim news

Subscribe on http://www.wakanim.tv for immediate access to your favorite programs!

* This application is at the moment reserved for our members who have a Wakanim account with subscription.
